reviewText: Good basic techniques. No-nonsense presentations. Similar to Krav Maga in many ways, but some subtle differences. Excellent production quality.
I purchased all 3 of the series. I love the way he breaks down the style- easy to learn, and no non-sense. If you want to learn the basics of knife fighting- get this program!
You need to watch the whole DVD. It begins slow, but picks up so just watch.

Quick simple reality based maneuvers to remember in case one is confronted by
unstable individuals. Stay safe out there.
